subject: Horse Racing
Rachel Alexandra (Race Horse)
Zenyatta (Race Horse)
lead_paragraph: After Rachel Alexandra finished second in the New Orleans Ladies Stakes on Saturday, her camp said she would not run against the unbeaten Zenyatta next month at Oaklawn.
